Rhonda Ross Kendrick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhonda_Ross_Kendrick 0 Rhonda Ross (born Rhonda Suzanne Silberstein; August 14, 1971) is an American singer-songwriter, actress, and public speaker. She is the daughter of singer/actress Diana Ross. She was born in Los Angeles and raised by Ross and her first husband, Robert Ellis Silberstein. Her biological father is Motown Records founder Berry Gordy. Rhonda_Ross ( born Rhonda_Suzanne_Silberstein ; August_14 , 1971 ) is an_American_singer-songwriter , actress , and public_speaker .
